Welcome to 
      Tavira Securities Limited is an agency broker specialising in global execution services for both equities and derivatives offering fully cross-margined multi-asset execution, custody & clearing service.
At Tavira our professional staff combine extensive experience with the latest technology to offer a flexible trading solution to meet client requirements.





Services We Offer

Agency Broking
Electronic Execution
